\newlabel{fig:sim-k}{{1}{2}{Effect of threshold $k$ on communicative success (simulation, marginalised over all other parameters). Lower $k$ (stricter threshold) reduces both orderings' success but narrows the gap between them. The incremental speaker maintains a consistent size-first advantage across $k$ values}{figure.1}{}}
