\newlabel{fig:production-empirical}{{7}{11}{Production empirical results. Utterance-type proportions (with bootstrapped 95\% CIs) by relevant-property condition and sharpness. Size-first orderings dominate in size-relevant contexts; colour-first orderings dominate in colour-relevant contexts. Only utterance types with $\geq 2\%$ in at least one condition are shown}{figure.7}{}}
